  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 300°F (150°C).",
    "Line a baking sheet with parchment paper. ",
    "Melt coconut oil and palm sugar in a saucepan over low heat, stirring occasionally. ",
    "Add candy melts and stir until melted and smooth. ",
    "Stir in coconut milk, lime juice, salt, vanilla extract, and tapioca starch until well combined. ",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5 minutes, stirring constantly. ",
    "Remove from heat and let cool slightly. ",
    "Stir in peanutsuntil well coated. ",
    "Drop by tablespoonfuls onto the prepared baking sheet. ",
    "Bake for 15-20 minutes or until cooked through and slightly firm to the touch. ",
    "Let cool completely on the baking sheet. ",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!"
  ],
